data.description: Introducing 10 Calle Plazuela, a 2-bedroom, 1.5 bathroom townhome nestled in the heart of Aldea de Santa Fe. Located 8 miles from the historical Santa Fe Plaza, this property presents an exceptional opportunity to live in a vibrant community surrounded by natural beauty and a plethora of amenities. As you step inside, you are greeted by an open and airy floor plan, thoughtfully designed to maximize space and functionality. On the main floor, enter an inviting living area, kitchen, bathroom, and laundry room with new floors and freshly painted walls. Upstairs, you will find both bedrooms with an abundance of natural light and beautiful evening sunset views from the front bedroom. From the kitchen into the backyard is a courtyard with mature trees, including an apple tree. A private patio awaits, ideal for al fresco dining or enjoying a morning cup of coffee. The meticulously landscaped courtyard offers a serene retreat where you can relax and rejuvenate amidst the picturesque surroundings. 10 Calle Plazuela is ideally located within the desirable Aldea community, known for its stunning views, 13 miles of walking trails, and a sense of tranquility. Aldea residents enjoy access to a community event plaza, clubhouse, tennis courts, and basketball courts, fostering a sense of community and an active lifestyle. Schedule a tour today!
